      Block
   =20
 =20
Honestly this is great:Square is renaming itself Block as it focuses on tec=
hnologies such as blockchain and expands beyond its original credit card-re=
ader business.Jack Dorsey=E2=80=99s payments giant said in an announcement =
that the new name, effective Dec. 10, =E2=80=9Cacknowledges the company=E2=
=80=99s growth=E2=80=9D and =E2=80=9Ccreates room for further growth.=E2=80=
=9D Block will still trade under the ticker SQ on the New York Stock Exchan=
ge.=E2=80=9CWe built the Square brand for our Seller business, which is whe=
re it belongs,=E2=80=9D Dorsey, cofounder and CEO, said in a statement. =E2=
=80=9CBlock is a new name, but our purpose of economic empowerment remains =
the same. No matter how we grow or change, we will continue to build tools =
to help increase access to the economy.=E2=80=9DI wish they had gone with =
=E2=80=9CCube=E2=80=9D but that wouldn=E2=80=99t get the blockchain referen=
ce in. This is real good. I hope Circle Internet Financial Limited=C2=A0wil=
l rebrand as=C2=A0Sphere. (Cylinder?)=C2=A0I look forward to Hypercube in 2=
033.
